# ğŸ† Snow Leopard Codex â€“ MySQL Portfolio Project

**Snow Leopard Codex** is a built-from-scratch MySQL relational database designed as a portfolio project to demonstrate core data engineering and database architecture skills.

This project includes:
- Schema design with primary and foreign key constraints
- Seed data insertion
- Relational queries using joins
- A full backup and restore workflow using MySQL CLI tools

The theme is intentionally playful and narrative-driven, while the implementation follows real-world database practices.

